Ask HN: Has anyone's Instagram business page marked as spam without a reason?
text:
I travelled from NL to US. The moment I opened out instagram business page, It got flagged as spam and was asked to verify page by writing some content into a page and taking the selfie. It also warns if this test fails then it will be disabled permanently disabled. There is no phone number where you can appeal this, there is no chat for instagram where you can appeal this.

Just because some automation decide to mark us as spam, we will end up losing all the audience, content and trust we had built via instagram. All our business is built via instagram. All content posted there is by me and it is not spam.

I was wondering if people where have faced this and how did you resolve it?

Tell HN: Chat.openai.com just restored all my old conversations
text:
While I'm under no illusion of privacy, I nevertheless found it slightly unsetteling. I am dilligently deleting every conversation I have had with the bot (mostly because I find it clutters up the UI)..

But today when I logged on, the side-bar is filled with "New chat" entries, every entry contains one of the conversations I've had, that I've deleted.
